{"tid":389816,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[屌教院sao老母]有關校園內展示標語 Campus Display","createTime":"2017-09-06T14:42:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T19:01:11.000Z","uid":44025,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8bea25fd43cd51c6fae1693553a13c7b4ee4c24d","tid":389816,"uid":44025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T14:42:13.000Z","msg":"各位同學︰<br />\n <br />\n有關校園內展示標語<br />\n <br />\n校方9月5日傍晚發現，蒙民偉圖書館對出圍欄以及B2民主牆展示有關「香港獨立」標語。《基本法》清楚列明，香港乃中國不可分離的部分。有關展示有違《基本法》，故已被移除。<br />\n<br />\n校方重申，校園設施（包括大學分配予學生組織的橫額展示區、告示版等）的使用者，當進行宣傳推廣及表達意見之用時，必須遵守相關法規及大學政策，否則校方會作出跟進措施。<br />\n<br />\n校方尊重學術自由，並呼籲大家繼續以理性、客觀和多元角度探討不同議題。<br />\n <br />\n物業處及學生事務處謹啟<br />\n2017年9月6日<br />\n <br />\nDear Students,<br />\n<br />\nSubject: Campus Display <br />\n <br />\nPlease be informed that actions were taken on the evening of 5 September to remove the banners and posters reading &ldquo;Hong Kong Independence&rdquo; outside the Mong Man Wai Library and on the Democracy Wall at B2.  &ldquo;Hong Kong Independence&rdquo; is in breach of the Basic Law, which stipulates that the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region is an inalienable part of the People&rsquo;s Republic of China.<br />\n <br />\nUsers of campus facilities, including display boards or banner sites allocated to student bodies for promotional purposes and expression of ideas, are reminded to adhere to the relevant statutory provisions, and university policies and regulations, otherwise the University reserves the right to take follow-up actions, as appropriate.<br />\n <br />\nAs a matter of principle, the University supports academic freedom, and we call for rationality, objectivity and multiple perspectives in the deliberation of different issues.<br />\n <br />\nEstates Office<br />\nStudent Affairs Office<br />\n6 September 2017"},{"pid":"901fabce25442a2b7b857b9ba1947f61ea42854f","tid":389816,"uid":119979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T14:49:37.000Z","m